@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'Outgoing Delivery Transporters'
define view entity zetr_ddl_i_outgoing_deltrns
  as select from    zetr_t_odti                                                    as Main
    left outer join DDCDS_CUSTOMER_DOMAIN_VALUE_T( p_domain_name: 'ZETR_D_TRNST' ) as TransporterType on  TransporterType.language  = $session.system_language
                                                                                                      and TransporterType.value_low = Main.trnst
  association to parent zetr_ddl_i_outgoing_deliveries as _outgoingDeliveries on $projection.DocumentUUID = _outgoingDeliveries.DocumentUUID
{
  key Main.docui           as DocumentUUID,
  key Main.trnst           as TransporterType,
  key Main.trnsp           as Transporter,
      TransporterType.text as TransporterTypeText,
      Main.title           as Title,
      Main.namef           as FirstName,
      Main.namel           as LastName,
      _outgoingDeliveries
}
